Package: MethyLasso
Type: Package
Title: MethyLasso: a segmentation approach to analyze DNA methylation patterns and identify differentially methylation regions from whole-genome datasets
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-07-20
Authors: Delphine Balaramane, Yannick Spill and Anais Flore Bardet
Maintainer: Anais Flore Bardet <bardeta@igbmc.fr>
Description: MethyLasso identifies low-methylated regions (LMRs), unmethylated regions (UMRs), DNA methylation valleys (DMVs) and partially methylated domains (PMDs) in a single condition as well as differentially methylated regions (DMRs) between two conditions
License: MIT
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.0), RcppEigen (>= 0.3.3.5.0)
